]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"c04c48",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Narrow coverage based on culture and sensitivity findings"
]
},
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"f78eb4",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Carbapenem or extended-range penicillin/Î²-lactamase inhibitor in most patients; in cases of septic shock (but not sepsis without shock), combination therapy with at least two antibiotics from different classes to cover the most likely bacterial pathogen"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
